# ORIG TITLE    Third night of rioting hits Stockholm suburbs . 
# ORIG CONTENT  Youths set fire to cars and buildings as rioting continued for a third night in the suburbs of Stockholm. Violence was reported in a number of areas.Emergency workers were also pelted with stones. Eight people are understood to have been arrested. The spate of unrest comes after police fatally shot a man in the largely immigrant suburb of Husby. He had reportedly threatened to kill officers with a machete. The disturbances started on Sunday when some 40 masked youths torched cars, a school and a launderette. 
